      "content": "It sounds like the ache of missing him is so deep that it feels like the only way to find peace is to escape the pain. The idea of letting go is a very heavy, very tempting thought when the grief is this overwhelming. If you are having thoughts of harming yourself, please reach out immediately to the 988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline by calling or texting 988. They are trained to support you through these intense feelings right now.",
